data.description: Nice corner lot in quiet Quail Ridge Landing, 3/2 Brick home with side entry garage and privacy fenced backyard. Plumbing fully replaced in 2019 to include new electric water heater, new dishwasher. 30 year dimensional shingle roof with Solar in 2020. Porcelain tile in kitchen, dining and baths. Luxury vinyl plank flooring in all bedrooms. Great location just blocks from the Oriole Beach boat ramp, parks, and more!
